上讲出失子故事，「让别人家参考，不要发生这样的悲剧。毕竟，很多孩子出了问题，家长从不在自己身上找原因」。一个中年人非要劝年轻人快乐"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c668379217d91675f590eb452dfda61e_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458209073"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIuc6R9NX12fchEAMaCDY0MTA0NTM4IPPW04QGMAA4XkAscgk0NTgyMDkwNzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1620903832.4106395", "card_id": "Q_59084436", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 278}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "珠宝行业有哪些不为人知的秘密？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "珠宝行业那些小秘密，各位大佬知道啊"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4f1cab5f641c7fdbbfab6f0d7c84a34_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "109 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/59084436"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iuc6R9NX12fchEAMaCDE1ODU2MDIwIMOlhsgFMAE4xCJALXIINTkwODQ0MzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1620903832.4111435", "card_id": "Q_351273101", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 471}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些在家比较容易做的美食？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "相关圈子→美食交流圈 - 知乎 因为疫情不能出门的你，如何在家安排自己的吃喝和生活？关注本期圆桌，看宅家生活的灵感撞击现场~ 在家也要好好生活 过程，配料比较简单的那种，我在家里做饭，太过于平常，但是有些好吃的又太麻烦，毕竟自己吃的，也不开饭店。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-82951b5a86f54a46bee8325f26cfc0bb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/351273101"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iuc6R9NX12fchEAMaCDQwMzM4NTQyIKLXpO0FMAA4gERALnIJMzUxMjczMTAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1620903832.4118676", "card_id": "Q_4564